<div>
  <div>
    <h1>
      Ask Ben - Step 2
    </h1>
    <h3>
      My Question: <%= @the_decision.name %>
    </h3>
    <h3>
      What criteria are important to you?
    </h3>
    <p> For example, if you're deciding where to eat dinner, some criteria that may be important is: price, quality, and ambiance. </p>

    <p> Also, weigh the criteria on how important it is to you (from 1 to 5) </p>
    <p> 1 means not important. 5 means extremely important </p>

    <div>
  <div>
    <table border="1">
      <tr>
        <th>
          Criteria
        </th>

        <th>
          Weight
        </th>

      </tr>

      <% @the_decision.criteria.each do |a_criterium| %>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <%= a_criterium.name %>
        </td>

        <td>
          <%= a_criterium.weight %>
        </td>

      </tr>
      <% end %>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>
    

    <form action="/insert_criterium" method="post">
      <div>
        <label for="name_box">
          Criteria:
        </label>

        <input type="text" id="name_box" name="query_name">
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="weight_box">Weight:</label>
          <select name="query_weight" id="weight_box">
            <option value="1">1</option>
            <option value="2">2</option>
            <option value="3">3</option>
            <option value="4">4</option>
            <option value="5">5</option>
          </select>
      </div>

  <hr>

      <div>
        <label for="decision_id_box">
        </label>

        <input type="hidden" id="decision_id_box" name="query_decision_id" value="<%= @the_decision.id %>">
      </div>

      <button>
        Create criteria
      </button>
    </form>

    <form action="/">
      

      <button>
        Done creating criteria
      </button>
    </form>



